Please find the assignment for test automation project to be sent for evaluation-

1. Using Playwright /Cypress + Cucumber BDD framework, create a new project on Git.
2. Add all required framework features to the project (Data driven, Keyword driven , POM etc)
3. Test Automate scenarios for following steps -
   1. Visit https://www.saucedemo.com/inventory.html.
   2. Add any item to cart and proceed to checkout, place order.
   3. Repeat the scenario for placing order on any other item.

Note : Test Automation Framework models must be followed and assertions should be placed on all the input fields. The code written should be executable.

Please send the git link once done on this email. Thanks.
